      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ITA KEEPING (1) flew the lids with a fast early split last time, hitting the frame with a 2.5 lengths second (17.51) over 300m at this track and making it two placings on end. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Key chance in this line up. MYSTIC PIXEL (5) was in the minors two back (17.41) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Has a good record here at this journey. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from four attempts. Has ability and is one of the better chances. ORANA MIA (8) was in traffic and missed the frame in a Grade 6 at this track over 300m latest, finishing a 4 length fourth (17.58). Has Box 8 this time where she has a win. Can do much better this time. DOONGALLA BAGGER (7) can feature with the right run.",
